  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/PackageDescription\/SupportedPlatform\/TVOSVersion\ncrawled: 2025-12-14T13:50:00Z\n---\n\n# SupportedPlatform.TVOSVersion\n\n**Structure**\n\nThe supported tvOS version.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstruct TVOSVersion\n```\n\n## Type Properties\n\n- **v10**: The value that represents tvOS 10.0.\n- **v11**: The value that represents tvOS 11.0.\n- **v12**: The value that represents tvOS 12.0.\n- **v13**: The value that represents tvOS 13.0.\n- **v14**: The value that represents tvOS 14.0.\n- **v15**: The value that represents tvOS 15.0.\n- **v16**: The value that represents tvOS 16.0.\n- **v17**: The value that represents tvOS 17.0.\n- **v18**: The value that represents tvOS 18.0.\n- **v26**: The value that represents tvOS 26.0.\n- **v9**: The value that represents tvOS 9.0.\n\n## Supporting tvOS\n\n- **tvOS(_:)**: Configures the minimum deployment target version for the tvOS platform.\n- **tvOS(_:)**: Configures the minimum deployment target version for the tvOS platform using a custom version string.\n- **tvOS**: The tvOS platform.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
